Package: InterconectaR
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2024-12-05
Title: Tools for Network Analysis and Psychometric Insights
Encoding: UTF-8
Authors@R: person("José", "Ventura-León",
                  email = "jventuraleon@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2996-4244"))
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
Description: A comprehensive package designed to facilitate network analysis
    and psychometric modeling in social sciences. It includes tools for
    constructing and analyzing psychological networks, calculating centrality
    and bridge metrics, and visualizing community structures. The package is
    optimized for comparing networks across groups and integrates advanced
    visualization techniques, making it ideal for educational, psychological,
    and social research.
